    "title": "Now Hiring Store Manager at Big Bazaar Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Big Bazaar Ventures Solutions. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Store Manager to strengthen our Allahabad-based team.\n\nAbout Big Bazaar Ventures Solutions:\nBig Bazaar Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Big Bazaar Ventures Solutions!",
